    <item>
      <title>卢比贬值对印度一些大型企业造成影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/rupee-pain-starts-to-show-as-india-s-top-airline-pummeled</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过两年的平静之后，卢比的突然下跌开始对印度企业的盈利造成压力，引发一些公司纷纷对冲货币风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/rupee-pain-starts-to-show-as-india-s-top-airline-pummeled</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
