    <item>
      <title>交易员寻找美联储线索，黄金价格领先美国 GDP 上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/gold-xauusd-holds-decline-after-powell-flags-pause-in-fed-easing-cycle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元下跌，黄金价格上涨，而美联储没有就下一步政策举措提供多少线索，投资者开始关注美国经济数据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-30/gold-xauusd-holds-decline-after-powell-flags-pause-in-fed-easing-cycle</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 Jan 2025 00:33:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国暗示加拿大和墨西哥可能避免征收关税，原油价格下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-30</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普挑选的商务部长表示，美国最大的原油供应国加拿大和墨西哥可能会避免高额关税，投资者等待美国贸易政策的明朗化，油价因此小幅走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-january-30</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 23:28:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>数据支持欧洲央行降息，股市因盈利而上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员等待苹果公司的业绩以及欧洲央行可能降息，欧洲股市和美国股指期货因一系列强劲的公司业绩而上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 22:30:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
